<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:12:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙失职：联合国秘书长古特雷斯必须下台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dereliction-of-duty-on-gaza-un-secretary-general-guterres-must-go/0000018c-33f2-dc03-a9ec-3ffb78620000</link><description>安东尼奥·古特雷斯在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后发表的评论遵循了一种充耳不闻的模式，不仅对此次袭击引发的地区性、潜在的全球性安全危机，而且对他更广泛的消极态度——这是联合国在世界舞台上的责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dereliction-of-duty-on-gaza-un-secretary-general-guterres-must-go/0000018c-33f2-dc03-a9ec-3ffb78620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女演员盖尔·加朵呼吁对哈马斯性暴力保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-actress-gal-gadot-calls-out-silence-over-sexual-based-violence-by-hamas/0000018c-347f-d5f2-a5cc-767fe34b0000</link><description>这位《神奇女侠》明星写道：“世界辜负了 10 月 7 日的女性，这是一个需要果断回应的紧急情况。”她与其他以色列和犹太女性一起强调了国际社会在谴责哈马斯暴行方面的犹豫不决</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 11:36:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-actress-gal-gadot-calls-out-silence-over-sexual-based-violence-by-hamas/0000018c-347f-d5f2-a5cc-767fe34b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙朋友的个人恳求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/a-personal-plea-from-a-friend-in-gaza/0000018c-3480-dc03-a9ec-3cfbc1670000</link><description>“我们真正需要的是推土机来挖掘并将我们深深地埋入我们的土地”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 11:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/a-personal-plea-from-a-friend-in-gaza/0000018c-3480-dc03-a9ec-3cfbc1670000</guid></item><item><title>弗吉尼亚州光明节烛光仪式因以色列和加沙紧张局势而取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hanukkah-candle-lighting-ceremony-in-virginia-cancelled-over-israel-gaza-tensions/0000018c-33d9-dc03-a9ec-3ffba2f20000</link><description>据弗吉尼亚半岛犹太联合社区称，活动组织者只有在加沙停火的呼吁下才同意恢复仪式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 10:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hanukkah-candle-lighting-ceremony-in-virginia-cancelled-over-israel-gaza-tensions/0000018c-33d9-dc03-a9ec-3ffba2f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何确定远方哈马斯扣押的人质的死亡？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-did-israel-determine-hamas-killed-hostages-left-in-gaza/0000018c-342a-dc03-a9ec-3c7bbf050000</link><description>为确定人质命运而建立的复杂而雄心勃勃的项目：一个新委员会正在观察、分析和比较视频剪辑，并使用支持证据和情报信息，以得出关键结论</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 10:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-did-israel-determine-hamas-killed-hostages-left-in-gaza/0000018c-342a-dc03-a9ec-3c7bbf050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质乔纳森·萨梅拉诺的家人得知他的死讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/family-of-israeli-hostage-jonathan-samerano-informed-of-his-death/0000018c-3406-d5f2-a5cc-761679a50000</link><description>这名 21 岁的男子从 Nova 音乐节逃往 Be&amp;#39;eri，随后在那里遭到枪杀和绑架</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 09:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/family-of-israeli-hostage-jonathan-samerano-informed-of-his-death/0000018c-3406-d5f2-a5cc-761679a50000</guid></item><item><title>本·格维尔任命的人员在枪支许可证上偷工减料后，枪支许可部门负责人辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/top-firearms-official-resigns-after-ben-gvirs-appointees-cut-corners-on-gun-permits/0000018c-33cb-da74-afce-b7fb542b0000</link><d