mizing-deaths-of-gazan-civilians-is-in-israels-best-interest/0000018c-3165-dc03-a9ec-3d7f8f000000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判恢复；利库德集团称其为“耻辱”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-to-resume-likud-mk-calls-it-a-disgrace/0000018c-3169-da74-afce-b5f9cfce0000</link><description>针对总理的案件因加沙战争中断两个月后将重新启动。据称，内塔尼亚胡采取了有利于 Bezeq 电信的监管措施，以换取对 Walla 网站（原由 Bezeq 拥有）的有利媒体报道</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 00:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-to-resume-likud-mk-calls-it-a-disgrace/0000018c-3169-da74-afce-b5f9cfce0000</guid></item><item><title>西方大国争论是否支持临时加沙缓冲区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-debate-whether-to-back-a-temporary-gaza-buffer-zone/0000018c-315f-d5f2-a5cc-775fa45b0000</link><description>以色列尚未澄清计划在该地区行动多久，以及是否计划在那里长期驻军。一位外交消息人士表示，“我们没有得到明确的答案，这引起了人们对这次行动的真正目的的担忧”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 00:38:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-debate-whether-to-back-a-temporary-gaza-buffer-zone/0000018c-315f-d5f2-a5cc-775fa45b0000</guid></item><item><title>外国消息人士称，以色列与哈马斯在不久的将来就释放人质达成协议的可能性很小</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/chances-slim-for-israel-hamas-agreement-on-hostage-releases-in-near-future/0000018c-3186-d5f2-a5cc-779636730000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡周日澄清说，以色列已停止与哈马斯讨论释放人质的问题。据国外消息人士称，双方恢复谈判“需要大量时间和精力”，且“气氛悲观”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 00:15:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/chances-slim-for-israel-hamas-agreement-on-hostage-releases-in-near-future/0000018c-3186-d5f2-a5cc-779636730000</guid></item><item><title>美国伪君子现在警告以色列要小心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-hypocrites-now-warn-israel-to-be-careful/0000018c-30fb-da74-afce-b5fb3b2d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:44:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-hypocrites-now-warn-israel-to-be-careful/0000018c-30fb-da74-afce-b5fb3b2d0000</guid></item><item><title>好战的以色列士兵的遗产和后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/legacies-and-consequences-of-trigger-happy-israeli-soldiers/0000018c-30fb-da74-afce-b5fb399b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/legacies-and-consequences-of-trigger-happy-israeli-soldiers/0000018c-30fb-da74-afce-b5fb399b0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-31ee-da74-afce-b5ffab120000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-31ee-da74-afce-b5ffab120000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡甚至没有关心“以色列英雄”死亡的细节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-even-bother-with-the-details-of-the-death-of-a-hero-of-israel/0000018c-312c-da74-afce-b5fd02010000</link><description>总理对尤瓦尔·凯斯特曼死亡情况的选择性言辞表明，即使在袭击发生 50 小时后，他也不知道到底发生了什么。真正引起他注意的是他的利库德集团成员：一群无知的罪犯</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 22:47:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-even-bother-with-the-details-of-the-death-of-a-hero-of-israel/0000018c-312c-da74-afce-b5fd02010000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯恐怖分子强奸的以色列妇女不应该需要标签</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-03/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-raped-by-hamas-terrorists-shouldnt-need-a-hashtag/0000018c-312c-d5f2-a5cc-773c2e490000</link><description>哈马斯性暴力的证据并不是为了在社交媒体上展开宣传活动。即使在它之后，它也不仅仅是一场运动</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 21:38:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-03/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-women-raped-by-hamas-terrorists-shouldnt-need-a-hashtag/0000018c-312c-d5f2-a5cc-773c2e490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列收紧指导方针，未受保护的学校恢复上课</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-toughens-guidelines-as-classes-at-unprotected-schools-resume/0000018c-313b-d5f2-a5cc-773f69de0000</link><description>以色列 80% 的教育设施受到保护，但这一数据掩盖了全貌，因为即使在受保护的机构中，受保护的空间也不足以容纳所有学生，而且有些距离教室太远</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 20:35:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-toughens-guidelines-as-classes-at-unprotected-schools-resume/0000018c-313b-d5f2-a5cc-773f69de0000</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷米雷任命前新纳粹分子为国家最高法律办公室主任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/argentinas-melei-appoints-former-neo-nazi-as-head-of-national-top-legal-office/0000018c-3023-da74-afce-b5fb4d9d0000</link><description>就任阿根廷总统不到两周后，这位自称“以色列粉丝”的人选择鲁道夫·巴拉（Rodolfo Barra）领导财政部检察办公室，尽管他此前因加入暴力反犹太主义团体而被迫辞去政府职务</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 17:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/argentinas-melei-appoints-former-neo-nazi-as-head-of-national-top-legal-office/0000018c-3023-da74-afce-b5fb4d9d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>